.SH "NAME"
cdist-type__postgres_role \- manage postgres roles
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
.sp
This cdist type allows you to create or drop postgres roles\&.
.SH "REQUIRED PARAMETERS"
.PP
state
.RS 4
either
\fIpresent\fR
or
\fIabsent\fR
.RE
.SH "OPTIONAL PARAMETERS"
.sp
All optional parameter map directly to the corresponding postgres createrole parameters\&.
.PP
password, login, createdb, createrole, superuser, inherit
.RS 4
EXAMPLES
.RE
